prompt:
Run the AutoPod multicam edit on the active timeline.

First, call `get_autopod_timeline_info` with:

  app_target: {{app_target}}

Review the discovered cameras + audio sources with the user in one short paragraph (camera count, mic count, total duration, FPS). If anything looks off (zero cameras, zero mics), stop and ask before proceeding.

Then call `run_autopod` with:

  app_target: {{app_target}}
  use_generative: {{use_generative}}
  fallback: {{fallback_track}}

Omit `fallback` if it is empty. After the run completes, summarize how many cuts were made and the resulting timeline name in one sentence.
